340
00:29:31,958 --> 00:29:35,666
Since our last guidance meeting,

341
00:29:36,166 --> 00:29:37,666
there's still no progress, Jo?

342
00:29:38,250 --> 00:29:39,416
No developments?

343
00:29:40,333 --> 00:29:42,500
If it's just a business plan

344
00:29:42,583 --> 00:29:45,083
that can't be applied,

345
00:29:45,166 --> 00:29:47,916
it means that this concept
has yet to be validated.

346
00:29:49,500 --> 00:29:52,833
You just need
one more supporting document.

347
00:29:54,000 --> 00:29:55,250
An investment letter.

348
00:29:56,125 --> 00:29:58,458
Evidence that shows

349
00:29:58,541 --> 00:30:03,166
an investor is interested in this plan.

350
00:30:05,541 --> 00:30:07,666
The deadline is close, Jo.

351
00:30:08,166 --> 00:30:10,625
You might not have enough time
for a review.

352
00:30:11,916 --> 00:30:13,291
Am I being clear, Jo?

353
00:30:13,916 --> 00:30:16,333
Do you understand what I'm saying?

354
00:30:16,416 --> 00:30:17,833
Yes, ma'am. I understand.

355
00:30:17,916 --> 00:30:18,916
Take this seriously.

356
00:30:20,125 --> 00:30:21,208
Okay.

